This release is the second version. It has six tasks. It implement a BLE transmission acknowledgement to increase transmission robustness.
UnifiedSignalTask for pin switch and ADC reading from FSR array.
SensorTask for IMU register reading.
ble_uart_task for BLE uart transmission in byte stream.
TaskDateTime for soft RTC.
ble_receive_task for receiving BLE uart string and received command processing.
dataMoveTask for move undelivered packet to resend buffer.
